What are we going to do exactly?

She's the kindest, smartest and most beautiful girl I know!

Why do you want to cleanse me as well?
The devil has you under his control. We need to cleanse your soul first.
You need to confess your sins.
Yes. Confess to Rekam'Ybab, my son.
